text: Soviet submarine S-363 (unofficial Swedish name: U137) was a Soviet submarine that ran aground outside the town of Karlskrona in Sweden on 27 October 1981. On 5 November the same year, it was led out of Swedish territorial waters. == References == ==Other websites== *Story of the incident with photos Category:1981 in Europe Category:1980s in Sweden Category:Cold War Category:1980s in the Soviet Union Category:Submarines
